com.apriori.collections

Class RandomAccessArrayBlockingDeque<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractList<E>
        • com.apriori.collections.RandomAccessArrayDeque<E>
          • com.apriori.collections.RandomAccessArrayBlockingDeque<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of element in the deque
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.concurrent.BlockingDeque<E>, java.util.concurrent.BlockingQueue<E>, java.util.Deque<E>, java.util.List<E>, java.util.Queue<E>, java.util.RandomAccess

    public class RandomAccessArrayBlockingDeque<E>
extends RandomAccessArrayDeque<E>
implements java.util.concurrent.BlockingDeque<E>
    A BlockingDeque implementation based on a RandomAccessArrayDeque. Like its super-class, it is based on a growable array and exposes random access operations on its contents.
